{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_06_01",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-05.m4a",
      "text": "私、まだ結婚するつもりなんてないからね！",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だいたい、誰からのプロポーズなの！？",
      "startTime": 4.6666667699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈……。誤解だ\n頼むから、俺の話を聞いてくれ",
      "startTime": 11.2999998807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-09.m4a",
      "text": "嫌！　{user}くんの話なんて",
      "startTime": 13.8999782324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "聞きたくない！　結婚だってしないんだから！",
      "startTime": 16.6333128373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、分かったから、頼む……！\n俺の説明が悪かった！",
      "startTime": 23.6666692178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "結婚じゃなくて、麻奈を広告塔にしたウエディング企画\nなんだ。インタビューやCM、グラビア撮影の仕事だよ",
      "startTime": 29.5000025511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-04.m4a",
      "text": "へ？　……仕事？　ウエディング、の？",
      "startTime": 34.4560802063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-04.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、へぇ……そう、なんだ？",
      "startTime": 39.0227446476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-02.m4a",
      "text": "紛らわしい言い方するから勘違いしちゃった",
      "startTime": 44.5227472542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sorry-01.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと聞かずに騒いじゃってごめんね",
      "startTime": 49.756081695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-11.m4a",
      "text": "でもさっきのは{user}くんが悪いよ！",
      "startTime": 54.556085165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "急に「ウエディングドレスを着ないか」なんて言うから",
      "startTime": 57.6560844869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-12.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　でも、ウエディングの仕事？",
      "startTime": 62.4560912684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-16.m4a",
      "text": "なんで？　私、まだ高校卒業したばっかりだよ",
      "startTime": 67.0560940659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ウエディングの仕事なんて勤まるかな？",
      "startTime": 72.3627513434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、少し前にバレンタインのCMに出ただろ？\nあれを先方が観て、ぜひ麻奈にお願いしたいって",
      "startTime": 80.0000124374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-06.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　あ、あのCM！？",
      "startTime": 84.4920759434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まだ恥ずかしいんだな……。でもこうして次の仕事に\n繋がるくらい好評だった、っていうことだよ",
      "startTime": 91.8000165063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-04.m4a",
      "text": "そっかー、そんなに求められちゃったら",
      "startTime": 95.7501317575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-05.m4a",
      "text": "応えない訳にもいかないよね！　やる！",
      "startTime": 99.3034645631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し真剣に考えてくれ。インタビューもあるんだぞ\n第一、結婚についてちゃんと考えたこと、あるのか？",
      "startTime": 108.1000109114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_no-02.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、正直……まだ考えたことないなぁ",
      "startTime": 112.5897627427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さっきも言ったけど、この間まで高校生だったし",
      "startTime": 116.6164315586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、せっかくのオファーだし、全力でやるよ",
      "startTime": 121.1897647771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "撮影までにはイメージを固めてくる。任せて",
      "startTime": 125.4430899622,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10056.90851179999,
          "startTime": 135.499998474
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈がそこまで言うなら、この仕事、受けよう\nじゃあ、これを書いておいてくれ",
      "startTime": 133.3333294943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-03.m4a",
      "text": "インタビューの事前アンケート？",
      "startTime": 136.2225173544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こんなに考えることがあるんだ、なんか凄いね",
      "startTime": 139.2666620889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、考えることは沢山あるだろ\n結婚は人生の一大イベントだし、節目でもあるんだから",
      "startTime": 146.6666546896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-13.m4a",
      "text": "それもそうだね。よし、任せといて",
      "startTime": 151.0780240288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-08.m4a",
      "text": "私は天才ちゃんだからね～。ふふん",
      "startTime": 154.4180148831,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3660.004091800005,
          "startTime": 158.0780189749
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（イメージを固めてくるとは言ってたが、ちょっと）\n（不安だな。まぁ本人がやる気だし、様子を見るか……）",
      "startTime": 164.3999931093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 170.8055477377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 172.0055436687
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_tired-01.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、{user}くん！",
      "startTime": 172.9722103032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-09.m4a",
      "text": "今日もレッスンよく頑張りました、私！",
      "startTime": 175.365544662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、麻奈。新しいステップ、良かったよ\n……で、そろそろ例のアンケートを回収したいんだけど",
      "startTime": 183.3000032818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-20.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん、よく聞いて",
      "startTime": 188.107631007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "結婚は人生の一大イベントなんだよ",
      "startTime": 190.5343057227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それは確か、俺が言った言葉だよな？",
      "startTime": 194.5743241221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-02.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ！　考えることが一杯あるの",
      "startTime": 197.6384736131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そして、真剣に考えるべきお仕事でもあるから……",
      "startTime": 200.9051555708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
